The Mind of a Chef - Season 4, Episode 1



Prune

With every chipped plate and hand-written to-do list, Gabrielle Hamilton's "presence" is all over her NYC restaurant, Prune. Enter the mind of chef Gabrielle Hamilton in the first episode of Season 4 of the Emmy-winning and James Beard Award-winning series THE MIND OF A CHEF.




Original Air Date: 05-Sep-2015
